Ramgate Changelog


All notable changes to ramgate are recorded here.  The format follows
Keep a Changelog (https://keepachangelog.com/), and the project adheres
to Semantic Versioning (https://semver.org/).


* Version 0.1.0 (2026-07-03)

** Added

  - Ramgate -- two-binary pure-Bash macOS memory tool (v0.1.0).

** Fixed

  - test: write the vm_stat stub to scratch; untrack the generated
    fixture.
  - Make "just ci" pass shellcheck (suppress false positives; fix
    SC2155 and SC2034).

** Changed

  - Shfmt-canonicalize all sources; move hooks scratch to $TMPDIR.

** Documentation

  - Compress to technical essentials; drop CONTRIBUTING and
    ARCHITECTURE; rumdl 190-column.

** Miscellaneous

  - license: relicense MIT -> AGPL-3.0-or-later.
  - Pseudonymize PII (contact, copyright, launchd label, fixture paths).
  - Strip the remaining contact email and a stale fixture path.
  - Drop the copyright line; fix a fixture path.
